data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, well kept four bedroom and two bath home on a beautiful half acre lot. This home offers a spacious living room and large kitchen perfect for everyone. Entering the huge master bathroom is a large jet tub, his and hers sinks, and a large walk-in closet. This home offers lots of storage and a large counter in the laundry room for folding clothes and extra storage. Outside you have a long ramp leading to the front door with a spacious porch, and out back there is a large covered deck and a 12x24 storage shed.  Don't miss this beautiful home, call a realtor today!
